day in and day out,\\\" International Olympic Committee President Thomas Bach said.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these difficult times\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"wars\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"conflicts\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"all the hate\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are longing for something which brings us together, something that is unifying, something that gives us hope.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic flame that we are lighting today is the symbol of this hope,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.793263748782002e-25, \"text\": \"Olympic flam